high_descs: Go one step to the right, turn left and turn left again so you are at the other side of the counter top.
Pick up the white cup on the counter top between the sink and the bottle.
Go to the microwave on the counter top.
Open the microwave, put the cup in it, heat it up for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the microwave.
Turn around, walk straight and go to the coffee maker on the counter top to your right.
Put the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated white cup on the coffee maker on the counter top.

high_descs: Turn left to face counter between microwave and sink.
Pick up coffee mug from counter to the left of the wine bottle
Open microwave door, place mug in, close door.  Wait three seconds, open microwave door, remove mug, close door.
Turn around, proceed across to counter, turn right to face counter with coffee machine on it.
anns.task_desc: Heat mug and place it on coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and face the counter to the right of the sink
Grab the white mug off of the counter
Back up and face the front of the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave and then take it out
Turn around and go to the coffee maker
Put the mug in the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Putting the white mug in the coffee maker
